<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:210'>　詩經疑問卷六　　　　　　元　朱倬　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='210:217'>　　　魯頌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='217:240'>魯侯爵也閟宫詩言乃命魯公俾侯于東詩中言公者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='240:263'>不一而足周禮諸公方五百里諸侯方四百里則爵土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='263:286'>不同也今公侯並稱豈二等之爵可通稱歟詩言公車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='286:309'>千乘集傳謂大國之賦適滿千乘而其地則三百一十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='309:332'>六里有竒也然則千乗之賦果儉於百里之魯歟抑諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='332:358'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='358:381'>侯方四百里之魯歟抑果曲阜地七百里之魯歟若是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='381:397'>者皆有司所不能無疑也幸悉言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='397:420'>　魯本侯爵言公者皆稱頌之辭故明言乃命魯公俾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='420:443'>　侯于東可見矣公侯二等之爵如周禮之說則不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='443:466'>　孟子則言公侯皆方百里也　百里千乘若以孟子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='466:489'>　萬取千千取百集註之說推之則包氏百里千乘之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='489:512'>　說不為無據朱子亦嘗疑孟子言周公封魯儉於百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='512:535'>　里則無緣有千乗車明堂位言以曲阜地七百里封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='535:561'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='561:584'>　周公於魯則又不啻千乗此極難解析然集傳據司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='584:607'>　馬法明言千乗之地方三百一十六里有竒又言大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='607:630'>　國之賦適滿千乘不容舉國盡行故大國止用三軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='630:653'>　然則魯之封域錫之山川土田附庸奄有龜蒙遂荒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='653:676'>　大東大東極東也豈儉於百里而已哉况僖公春秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='676:699'>　之魯也孟子時去春秋不逺已明言今魯方百里者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='699:715'>　五凡此皆着引用推而通之可也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='715:738'>魯之有頌本非禮矣魯祖周公禮之宜也今閟宫一詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='738:764'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='764:787'>上紀姜源后稷太王文武之事且以皇皇后帝皇祖后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='787:810'>稷郊祀配天之禮堂堂言之禮歟夫子刪詩而在所不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='810:820'>去豈作春秋之意歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='820:843'>　詩人之論自源徂流故雖頌魯僖而上及乎后稷太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='843:866'>　王文武周公之事明其源本之所自出也因成王賜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='866:889'>　周公以天子禮樂故遂以夏正孟春郊祀上帝而以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='889:912'>　后稷配之然非禮矣魯人據其實而頌之夫子因其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='912:935'>　舊而存之豈非春秋據事直書而善惡自見之義歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='935:961'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='961:984'>魯閟宫篇曰春秋匪解享祀不忒皇皇后帝皇祖后稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='984:1007'>享以騂犧謂魯得郊祀也傳者謂命魯公以夏正孟春</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1007:1030'>郊祀上帝配以后稷牲騂牡禮郊以冬至非春秋時禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1030:1041'>也傳文以為孟春何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1041:1048'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1048:1051'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1051:1074'>閟宫言王曰叔父建爾元子俾侯于魯是成王封伯禽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1074:1097'>于魯明矣孟子乃言周公之封於魯史記亦言武王封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1097:1123'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1123:1146'>周公于曲阜然則封魯者成王歟抑武王歟受封者周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1146:1169'>公歟抑伯禽歟閟宫言大啓爾字為周室輔錫之山川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1169:1192'>土田附庸明堂位亦曰成王封周公地方七百里革車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1192:1215'>千乘是大國也周禮則曰諸侯之地方四百里孟子則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1215:1228'>曰周公封魯儉於百里何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1228:1235'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1235:1261'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1261:1268'>　　　商頌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1268:1291'>商之髙宗周之宣王皆中興之君也商有祀髙宗之樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1291:1302'>周無祭宣王之詩何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1302:1323'>　詩經夫子刪定有之者不容除無之者無所攷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1323:1346'>長發一詩朱子謂宜為祫祭之詩祫則合太祖而下羣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1346:1369'>廟之上皆祭也而詩中獨稱契相土成湯三君何歟未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1369:1378'>及於伊尹又何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1378:1401'>　祫雖合羣廟之主而祭之而以肈基之主與顯王言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1401:1427'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1427:1441'>　之亦足矣豈能一一及之乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1441:1465'>　猶𤣥鳥言契之生以及成湯閟宫言后稷太王以及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1465:1473'>　文武周公也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1473:1496'>　蘇氏引商書曰兹予大享于先王爾祖其從與享之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1496:1519'>　是禮也豈其起於商之世歟猶周詩言文武受命而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1519:1527'>　及於召公也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1527:1550'>長發一篇朱子疑為祫祭之詩果何以知非禘祭之詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1550:1553'>歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1553:1579'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1579:1602'>　禘者祭始祖所自出之帝而以始祖配之故商人禘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1602:1625'>　嚳而郊㝠祖契而宗湯此詩若以為禘祭則當但言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1625:1648'>　嚳與契而已今乃不及嚳而始於契且及相土而至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1648:1671'>　于成湯其非禘祭明矣蓋祫祭者合已毁未毁之主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1671:1694'>　而祭于太祖之廟也今由契而至湯凡十四君此詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1694:1713'>　乃該首尾而言之其為祫祭之詩無疑矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1713:1736'>稷契皆未嘗有天下也而詩人於稷曰奄有下土纉禹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1736:1759'>之緒於契曰受小國是達受大國是達何歟且契敷敎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1759:1785'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1785:1801'>者也而以𤣥王桓撥稱之又何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1801:1824'>　奄有下土纉禹之緒謂后稷敎民稼穡於禹平水土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1824:1830'>　之後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1830:1853'>　受小國大國謂天下無不歸心於敷敎之聖人也契</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1853:1876'>　敷敎於百姓不親五品不遜之時故不得不以桓武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1876:1883'>　撥治之歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1883:1906'>不剛不柔長發所以頌湯也柔亦不茹剛亦不吐烝民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1906:1929'>所以美仲山甫也剛柔不可失於一偏尚矣而衞武公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1929:1955'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1955:1978'>自警之辭曰無不柔嘉崧髙之美申伯曰柔惠且直仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1978:1998'>山甫之德亦以柔嘉言之又每以柔為尚何歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1998:2021'>　文蔚問此以柔嘉維則稱仲山甫崧髙以柔惠且直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2021:2044'>　稱申伯然則入德之方其可知矣曰如此則乾卦不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2044:2067'>　用得了人之資質自有柔德勝者自有剛德勝者如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2067:2090'>　宋朝范文正公富鄭公輩是以剛德勝范忠宣范淳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2090:2113'>　夫趙清獻蘇子容輩是以柔德勝只是他柔却柔得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2113:2136'>　好如仲山甫令儀令色小心翼翼却是柔袒其中自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2136:2162'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2162:2185'>　有骨子不是一向如此柔去人看文字要得言外之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2185:2208'>　意若以仲山甫柔嘉維則必要為入德之方則不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2208:2221'>　人之進德須用剛健不息</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2221:2245'>契有𤣥王之稱湯有武王之號文王又有平王之稱何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2245:2260'>名號之不一而皆不見於他經歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2260:2267'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2267:2290'>商周之先稷契同居有虞之世何以自契至湯十有四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2290:2303'>世自稷至王季以十四世耶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2303:2329'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0031', 'WYG', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2329:2336'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2336:2359'>殷武之詩曰奮伐荆楚又曰維女荆楚居國南鄉按周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2359:2382'>成王時始封熊繹於荆周惠王時為魯僖公元年始冇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2382:2396'>楚號商之高宗乃伐荆楚何耶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2396:2403'>　<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
